name: ALL THINGS WINTER
description:
An ode to winter and staying under the covers. 

This is a print inspired by my favourite grey and cold season, and long hours spent in bed with a good book. 

The little details:

* The print measures 15x20cm.

* It is a digital photographic print professionally printed on Fuji Crystal Archive Photo Paper with a matt finish.

* All items are shipped out approximately 4-7 days after an order is placed in order to allow time to print them out. 

* All prices are in Australian dollars/AUD.

* To see a larger image of this print, visit here: http://www.flickr.com/photos/28728348@N06/4947454038/in/set-72157624853309256/

I welcome any questions :)
